    <section id="id-073632681232">
      <title>Frequency response of systems in cascade or in parallel</title>
      <para id="id6016684">In various situations filters are connected in cascade or in parallel, and we would like to know the overall frequency response. By using the associativity and the distributivity of impulse responses, and the convolution theorem of DTFT we can obtain (Fig.3.34):</para>
